Template: wargus/extractdata
Type: multiselect
Choices: extract Warcraft II basic data, extract Warcraft II videos, extract Warcraft II basic data + Beyond the Dark Portal data, extract Warcraft II additional sound tracks (original CD-ROM only)
Default: extract Warcraft II basic data
Description: 
 You need to provide original Warcraft II data for Wargus to use it. If you don't, Wargus will use the builtin Aleona's Tales dataset. Processing of some of the following options may take a couple of minutes.

Template: wargus/cdpath
Type: string
Default: /media/cdrom
Description: 
 Path to Warcraft II data: 

Template: wargus/expcdpath
Type: string
Default: /media/cdrom
Description: 
 Path to Warcraft II Beyond the Dark Portal data: 

Template: wargus/nodataBasic
Type: error
Description: 
 Couldn't find Warcraft II data on the specified path. Try again.

Template: wargus/nodataExpansionPack
Type: error
Description: 
 Couldn't find Warcraft II Beyond the Dark Portal data on the specified path. Try again.

